BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:eBTscJhLYVgAJitIlEjAW
SUMMARY:Loose Cannons Improv
DTSTAMP:20260323T022346Z
DTSTART:20260327T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Thursdays from 8pm - 9:30pm Loose Cannons is Seattle improv at 
	its most unpredictable. Every performance at Unexpected Productions in Pik
	e Place Market is a one-of-a-kind experience: exciting\, unexpected\, a li
	ttle dangerous\, and always ridiculously fun. This is the show where anyth
	ing can happen and usually does. Part One: Part One: The night kicks off w
	ith a unique performance\, setting the performers in a new format with spe
	cial guest improvisers showcasing their signature style or a never-before-
	seen format. Your suggestions fuel the fire\, and the improvisers will ign
	ite the stage\, bringing your ideas to life. Part Two: The second half lau
	nches from a single audience suggestion\, setting the performers in motion
	. It might start with a song\, a monologue\, or a rapid-fire group connect
	ion game. Whatever emerges will inspire spontaneous stories\, surprising t
	wists\, and big comedic swings. Loose Cannons is fueled by audience ideas\
	, fearless performers\, and the thrill of not knowing what hap\n\nhttps://
	www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/loose-cannons-improv-2/?occurrence
	=2026-03-26
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/loose-cannons-improv-2/
	?occurrence=2026-03-26
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kBEHmBJTqkJ5tnBmxK8lZ
SUMMARY:Insider’s Breakfast and Culture Tour of Pike Place Market
DTSTAMP:20260323T022346Z
DTSTART:20260327T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:VOTED 10 BEST FOOD TOURS IN THE COUNTRY BY USA TODAY! Get ahead
	 of peak crowds and join Savor Seattle as they take you behind the scenes 
	on an early-morning exploration of Pike Place Market. Their guides on this
	 tour are deeply rooted members of the Market community who will truly tak
	e you to “Meet The Producer” using their years of experience in the neighb
	orhood. This is an experience you cannot get with any regular tour guide! 
	Feel like a local as you walk and eat your way through the best morning bi
	tes! Learn the names and stories of the people who operate the businesses 
	Seattle Savor's is honored to highlight as their guides give you the full 
	history of how Pike Place became The Soul of Seattle. "Watching the Market
	 come to life is a time-honored Seattle tradition we would love for you to
	 witness as we share our years of expertise with you. Come savor mornings 
	at Pike Place Market!" Tours are available on Monday\, Thursday\, Friday\,
	 Saturday and Sunday from 8am - 10:30pm Book a Tour \n\nhttps://www.pikepl
	acemarket.org/events-calendar/insiders-breakfast-and-culture-tour-of-pike-
	place-market/?occurrence=2026-03-27
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/insiders-breakfast-and-
	culture-tour-of-pike-place-market/?occurrence=2026-03-27
LOCATION:Pike Place Market
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT14H30M
END:VEVENT
